author: @CosmicWin
text:
In these set of outfits, there is only two pairs of similar/matching clothes:

Pair 1: Nayeon, Momo
Pair 2: Jihyo, Mina

The other members have very similar color schemes to other members but the outfits stand alone. As far as color schemes, everyone is meant to stay into a group of colors except for Dahyun, who stand out the most due to her difference in colors. Here are the color groups:

Group 1: Momo, Sana, Chaeyoug, Tzuyu
Group 2: Nayeon, Jihyo, Mina

As you can tell, everyone belongs to a color scheme except for Dahyun. And as far as patterns go, everyone but Sana, Chaeyoung and Tzuyu are wearing plaid which makes Sana, Chaeyoung and Tzuyu stand out the most overall, with Sana wearing checkered patterns, Chaeyoung choosing a diamond pattern, and Tzuyu wearing a variety of layers with the see-through layer being striped.
